@startuml
title pyArchimate Deployment Diagram

node DeveloperWorkstation {
  node "Python 3.10+ runtime" as PythonRuntime
  artifact "pyArchimate CLI" as CLI
  artifact "pyArchimate Core" as Library
}
node CIRunner {
  node "CI Python runtime" as PyCI
  artifact "pyArchimate CLI" as CLI_CI
  artifact "pyArchimate Core" as Library_CI
}
node Filesystem {
  artifact "Archi / ARIS sources" as Sources
  artifact "Exchange Formats (XML, CSV)" as Exports
}
node Logging {
  artifact "pyArchimate logs" as Logs
}
node Dependencies {
  artifact "lxml / oyaml / pillow" as Deps
}
actor "Designer" as Designer
actor "Automation / CI" as Automation

Designer --> CLI : runs scripts
Automation --> CLI_CI : triggers CI pipelines
CLI --> Library : imports public API
CLI_CI --> Library_CI : imports public API
Library --> Deps : leverages dependencies
Library_CI --> Deps
Library --> Sources : reads source data
Library_CI --> Sources
Library --> Logs : emits warnings/errors
Library_CI --> Logs
Library --> Exports : writes output files
Library_CI --> Exports
@enduml
